'''神經發炎'''（Neuroinflammation）是指[[神經組織|神經組織]]的[[發炎反應|發炎反應]]，可能為[[感染|感染]]、[[創傷性腦損傷|創傷性腦損傷]]、有毒物質或[[自體免疫疾病|自體免疫疾病]]所致<ref name=":2">Ebert SE, Jensen P, Ozenne B, Armand S, Svarer C, Stenbaek DS ''et al.'' Molecular imaging of neuroinflammation in patients after mild traumatic brain injury: a longitudinal 123 I-CLINDE SPECT study. ''Eur J Neurol'' 2019. doi:10.1111/ene.13971.</ref><ref name=Gendelman>{{cite journal | vauthors = Gendelman HE | title = Neural immunity: Friend or foe? | journal = Journal of Neurovirology | volume = 8 | issue = 6 | pages = 474–9 | date = December 2002 | pmid = 12476342 | doi = 10.1080/13550280290168631 }}</ref>。因免疫細胞一般無法穿越[[血腦障壁|血腦障壁]]，[[中樞神經系統|中樞神經系統]]（[[腦|腦]]與[[脊髓|脊髓]]）是[[免疫豁免|免疫豁免區]]<ref>{{cite journal | vauthors = Das Sarma J | title = Microglia-mediated neuroinflammation is an amplifier of virus-induced neuropathology | journal = Journal of Neurovirology | volume = 20 | issue = 2 | pages = 122–36 | date = April 2014 | pmid = 23979705 | doi = 10.1007/s13365-013-0188-4 }}</ref>，但中樞神經系統中負責清除異物的[[小膠質細胞|小膠質細胞]]與[[星狀細胞|星狀細胞]]、[[內皮細胞|內皮細胞]]等皆可釋放多種促進發炎反應的[[細胞激素|細胞激素]]（[[白细胞介素-6|白细胞介素-6]]、{{le|白血球介素-1β|Interleukin 1 beta}}、[[腫瘤壞死因子-α|腫瘤壞死因子-α]]等）<ref name=TBI>{{cite journal | vauthors = Mayer CL, Huber BR, Peskind E | title = Traumatic brain injury, neuroinflammation, and post-traumatic headaches | url = https://archive.org/details/sim_headache_2013-10_53_9/page/n132 | journal = Headache | volume = 53 | issue = 9 | pages = 1523–30 | date = October 2013 | pmid = 24090534 | doi = 10.1111/head.12173 | pmc=4089888}}</ref><ref name=":2" /> ，為正常[[神經調節|神經調節]]的機制之一，而當神經發生感染或創傷時，這些細胞可能持續分泌細胞激素造成急性發炎，使血腦障壁出現破口而吸引血液中的淋巴球前來<ref name="pmid32423330">{{cite journal | vauthors = Ren H, Han R, Chen X, Liu X, Wan J, Wang L, Yang X, Wang J | title =  Potential therapeutic targets for intracerebral hemorrhage-associated inflammation: An update | journal = J Cereb Blood Flow Metab | year= 2020 | pmid = 32423330 | doi = 10.1177/0271678X20923551 }}</ref>。神經發炎可能有助於修復受損的神經組織<ref name="pmid30874626">{{cite journal| author=Yong HYF, Rawji KS, Ghorbani S, Xue M, Yong VW| title=The benefits of neuroinflammation for the repair of the injured central nervous system. | journal=Cell Mol Immunol | year= 2019 | volume= 16 | issue= 6 | pages= 540-546 | pmid=30874626 | doi=10.1038/s41423-019-0223-3 | pmc=6804643 | url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/eutils/elink.fcgi?dbfrom=pubmed&tool=sumsearch.org/cite&retmode=ref&cmd=prlinks&id=30874626  }} </ref>

[[阿茲海默症|阿茲海默症]]、[[帕金森氏症|帕金森氏症]]與[[多發性硬化症|多發性硬化症]]等神經疾病的致病機理皆可能與神經發炎有關。阿茲海默症的病因過去多認為[[Tau蛋白|Tau蛋白]]堆積造成的{{le|神經纖維纏結|Neurofibrillary tangle}}及[[β淀粉样蛋白|β淀粉样蛋白]]堆積造成的[[老年斑|老年斑]]，近年也有理論認為神經發炎可能是致病原因<ref name="Alzheimer's">{{cite journal | vauthors = Meraz-Ríos MA, Toral-Rios D, Franco-Bocanegra D, Villeda-Hernández J, Campos-Peña V | title = Inflammatory process in Alzheimer's Disease | journal = Frontiers in Integrative Neuroscience | volume = 7 | pages = 59 | date = August 2013 | pmid = 23964211 | doi = 10.3389/fnint.2013.00059 | pmc=3741576}}</ref><ref name="pmid33364931">{{cite journal |vauthors=Culibrk RA, Hahn MS |title=The Role of Chronic Inflammatory Bone and Joint Disorders in the Pathogenesis and Progression of Alzheimer's Disease |journal=Frontiers in Aging Neuroscience |volume=12 |pages=583884 |date=2020 |pmid=33364931 |pmc=7750365 |doi=10.3389/fnagi.2020.583884}}</ref>；帕金森氏症的致病機理長期以來都被認為與神經發炎有關<ref name="Tansey parkinson's">{{cite journal | vauthors = Barnum CJ, Tansey MG | title = Neuroinflammation and non-motor symptoms: the dark passenger of Parkinson's disease? | journal = Current Neurology and Neuroscience Reports | volume = 12 | issue = 4 | pages = 350–8 | date = August 2012 | pmid = 22580742 | doi = 10.1007/s11910-012-0283-6 }}</ref>；多發性硬化症則是免疫細胞攻擊腦部或脊髓神經元的[[髓鞘|髓鞘]]，造成其{{tsl|en|Demyelinating disease|去髓鞘疾病|去髓鞘}}，並刺激小膠質細胞釋放細胞激素以致神經發炎<ref name="Tansey parkinson's" />。

